# Docs: /docs is scratch (gitignored by default), /docs/public is the commit zone.
# Scratch docs (plans, research, drafts, debates, specs) go directly in /docs —
# they're ignored by the blanket rule and never committed. Docs that should ship
# in the public OSS export live in /docs/public/.
docs/*
!docs/public/

